en_743283_0	A selected batch of 384 more potential Army retirees, including two Officers, expecting to receive vocational training shortly, prior to their retirement attended an introductory workshop that went on for a week (June 25 - July 02) at Saliyawewa Centre for Army Vocational Training (CAVT).
en_743283_1	The 7 day long initial workshop ended after a brief ceremony.
en_743283_2	Representing the Commandant, CAVT, Lieutenant Colonel Shashika Perera, Commanding Officer, CAVT, Chief Instructor, CAVT and several officers attended the closing ceremony and contributed to the event giving concluding remarks.
